verbose_text: O6-methylguanine DNA methyltransferase (MGMT) promoter methylation being a predictive marker of benefit from temozolomide irradiation treatment, we next analyzed whether the prognosis value associated with the phosphorylation level of H3T6, H3S10 and H3Y41 is influenced or not by the MGMT methylation status XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR.
